data.description: Beautiful home completely remodeled with 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Great location! Second kitchen and second laundry room in basement! Close to shopping, close to schools, close to restaurants, and close to I-20. This gorgeous quality renovated dwelling has an open concept on the upper level, bamboo flooring, custom white 36-inch shaker cabinets, an oversized island with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an eat-in kitchen just off the recently renovated deck. Walk-in pantry and laundry room. This floor plan flows nicely with a view from the kitchen to the family and dining rooms. The spacious family room has a vaulted ceiling and a fireplace. Large separated dining room. Oversized master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and walk-in closet. Master bathroom counts with a separate shower, soaking tub, double vanity, and upgraded beautiful tile. The two additional upper-level bedrooms have ceiling fans and an updated bathroom. The lower level is completely finished with an exterior entrance, 2 bedrooms, a family room area, and LVP flooring. Separated kitchen, separated closet laundry, and full updated bathroom. Call now for a private showing. Talk to your agent about seeing this one! You will not be disappointed!
